- [Man] Good-bye.

15:03.861 --> 15:06.362
- Darling, the flowers.
- Good luck.

15:08.616 --> 15:11.451
- Paul, my hat's in your hand.
- Good-bye.

15:11.535 --> 15:13.536
See you there.

15:41.357 --> 15:43.691
What astonishing bad luck...

15:43.776 --> 15:47.111
that in the whole of London
they could find no flat to rent...

15:47.196 --> 15:49.822
except the one bottled right up
against our library window.

15:49.907 --> 15:52.075
Who could find no flat?

15:52.159 --> 15:55.495
Tibby, the Wilcoxes.

15:55.579 --> 16:00.333
Surely even you remember that business
last summer with Helen and Paul Wilcox.

16:00.417 --> 16:02.335
Paul Wilcox.

16:02.419 --> 16:05.129
