17:15.159 --> 17:18.161
They've only taken the flat
for a few weeks, the porter said.

17:21.999 --> 17:24.500
Do we bow,
or do we cut them dead?

17:25.502 --> 17:27.753
Darling...

17:27.838 --> 17:29.797
why don't you take up
Cousin Frieda's invitation...

17:29.882 --> 17:32.300
